Create Total Crime, Total Arrest and Crime Rate by Quarter Visualization 17



 Create Total Crime, Total Arrest and Crime Rate by Quarter Visualization(ChicagoCrimeData)

  1. Click on Line and clustered column visualization
  2. Drag OccurredDate  Date Hierarchy to the Shared axis and delete year and day from the hierarchy.
  3. Drag DOW column below the Hierarchy in the  shared axis
  4. Drag TotalCrime  and Total Arrest Measures to the Column values field
  5. Drag CrimeRate Measure to the Line value field
  6. in the Formatting pane: Y-Axis- Switch off Title before turning off, X-Axis- Switch off the title, Switch on Data Label, Title- Text =  Total Crime, Total Arrest and Crime Rate by Quarter, font color = white,background-color = blue, Centre alignment
